WEBVTT

00:00:27.992 --> 00:00:30.025
na sisi kama raia

00:00:30.049 --> 00:00:33.750
tunahitaji kuanza kuelewa
kua tuna jukumu kubwa

00:00:33.774 --> 00:00:37.600
kwenye kuunda jinsi dunia
itakavyotawaliwa kusonga mbele.

00:00:37.624 --> 00:00:41.891
Kweli kabisa, mvutano wa sasa
ni kati ya serikali,

00:00:41.915 --> 00:00:44.985
zilizopoteza nguvu zao nyingi kwa
makampuni

00:00:45.009 --> 00:00:49.267
kwa sababu intaneti haijajengwa
karibu na mfumo wa taifa la taifa

00:00:49.291 --> 00:00:51.331
kote ambayo serikali zina nguvu.

00:00:51.355 --> 00:00:53.212
Intaneti ni ya mataifa.

00:00:53.236 --> 00:00:56.275
Sio ya kimataifa,
na sio ya kitaifa,

00:00:56.299 --> 00:00:59.389
na kwa sababu hiyo makampuni
yamekua na nguvu sana.